snippet.title: Wild City - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wild City is a Roguelike Ecosystem Builder where cards are living organisms that can synergize and prey on each other.
Place your cards on an expanding board to trigger satisfying chain-reactions and shape an interconnected ecosystem.

- Wishlist NOW on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2436970/Wild_City/
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/MonkaStudioss
- Join our discord: https://discord.gg/QTMXpmgpqX
